title: 31: Trevor Gets Invited to a Sex Party
itunes:title: Trevor Gets Invited to a Sex Party
description:
Allllllright this one is INSANE. Trev and Mike do a deep dive into the sex robot world, they riff about girls flashing mountains, and they answer the age old question: would you sniff your dog's ass? Finally, Michael says something so outrageous that Trevor walks off the show. Honestly... rightfully so.
